node.text: Thanks for having me this morning @livekellyandryan 😀... was a blast showing you some of my favorite kitchen tools & discussing our new @lebernardinny @cityharvestnyc initiative...Beginning when we reopen on March 17th, 5$ will be donated for every guest who dines with us to @cityharvestnyc to help feed Hungry NYers (5$ helps feed 13 NYers for day)!! 🙏🏼 Find info on @cityharvestnyc ‘s food rescue efforts ➡️ cityharvestnyc.org 💚🤍💚 #WeAreCityHarvest

COVID-19 VACCINATION PROTOCOL UPDATE …starting August 4th, @lebernardinny will require proof of vaccination for every guest (in addition to our already 100% vaccinated team)… safety remains our priority. 
#Repost @lebernardinny 
LUNCH AND OTHER IMPORTANT NEWS!
We are delighted to reopen for lunch on Wednesday, September 15th…our lunch hours will be Wednesday-Friday 12:00pm-1:30pm (beginning in October Monday-Friday). Starting this Wednesday, August 4th we will require proof of COVID-19 vaccination upon arrival at the restaurant. 
.
Reservations for lunch are now available at 212-554-1515 or online via @resy . Proof of vaccination includes a physical Covid-19 vaccine card, a New York State Excelsior Pass, a relevant state-provided vaccine pass, or a photo of your vaccination card.

CLEANSING !!
Weekend ritual: tea made w garden herbs and bit of honey.
1pinch sage
1pinch thyme
1pinch mint
1pinch Rosemary
1pinch fennel
1pinch parsley 
1pinch oregano 
Infuse herbs w simmering water in tea pot for +-10 minutes…Strain & add bit of local honey …ENJOY!!
